SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill 2114 as follows:
1. On Page 9, Line 14, by inserting, after the word “A” and before the word “violation”, the words, “first
violation of this section shall result in the issuance of a warning. A second and subsequent”;
2. On Page 10, Line 9 1/2, by inserting after the period, the following language:
“F. This section shall not apply to unintentional or momentary crossing of property boundaries
where a person is making reasonable efforts to recover a dog on land they do not own.”
